msgid "About Us - Convertica"
msgstr "Tentang Kami - Convertica"

msgid ""
"Free online PDF tools platform providing conversion, editing, and "
"organization services."
msgstr ""
"Platform alat PDF online gratis yang menyediakan layanan konversi, "
"pengeditan, dan organisasi."

msgid "Today better than yesterday, tomorrow better than today"
msgstr "Hari ini lebih baik dari kemarin, besok lebih baik dari hari ini"

msgid "About Convertica"
msgstr "Tentang Convertica"

msgid "Your trusted partner for all PDF document needs"
msgstr "Mitra terpercaya Anda untuk semua kebutuhan dokumen PDF"

msgid "Mission icon"
msgstr "Ikon misi"

msgid "Our Mission"
msgstr "Misi Kami"

msgid ""
"At Convertica, we believe in the power of continuous improvement. Our "
"mission is to provide you with the most reliable, fast, and user-friendly "
"PDF tools available online. We understand that your documents are important, "
"and we're committed to ensuring that every interaction with our platform "
"exceeds your expectations."
msgstr ""
"Di Convertica, kami percaya pada kekuatan perbaikan berkelanjutan. Misi kami "
"adalah menyediakan alat PDF yang paling andal, cepat, dan ramah pengguna "
"yang tersedia online. Kami memahami bahwa dokumen Anda penting, dan kami "
"berkomitmen untuk memastikan bahwa setiap interaksi dengan platform kami "
"melebihi harapan Anda."

msgid "Growth icon"
msgstr "Ikon pertumbuhan"

msgid "Our Core Principle: Constant Improvement"
msgstr "Prinsip Inti Kami: Perbaikan Berkelanjutan"

msgid "We live by a simple yet powerful philosophy:"
msgstr "Kami hidup dengan filosofi yang sederhana namun kuat:"

msgid ""
"Today, we are better than we were yesterday. Tomorrow, we will be even "
"better than today."
msgstr ""
"Hari ini kami lebih baik dari kemarin. Besok kami akan lebih baik lagi dari "
"hari ini."

msgid ""
"This isn't just a slogan—it's our commitment to you. Every day, our team "
"works tirelessly to enhance our platform, improve our tools, and refine the "
"user experience. We listen to your feedback, analyze usage patterns, and "
"implement improvements that make Convertica more powerful, intuitive, and "
"reliable."
msgstr ""
"Ini bukan hanya slogan—ini adalah komitmen kami kepada Anda. Setiap hari, "
"tim kami bekerja tanpa lelah untuk meningkatkan platform kami, memperbaiki "
"alat kami, dan menyempurnakan pengalaman pengguna. Kami mendengarkan umpan "
"balik Anda, menganalisis pola penggunaan, dan mengimplementasikan perbaikan "
"yang membuat Convertica lebih kuat, intuitif, dan andal."

msgid ""
"Whether it's optimizing our conversion algorithms, adding new features, "
"improving security, or enhancing performance, we never stop striving for "
"excellence. This dedication to continuous improvement means that when you "
"use Convertica, you're always getting the best version of our platform—and "
"we're already working on making it even better."
msgstr ""
"Baik itu mengoptimalkan algoritma konversi kami, menambahkan fitur baru, "
"meningkatkan keamanan, atau meningkatkan kinerja, kami tidak pernah berhenti "
"berusaha untuk mencapai keunggulan. Dedikasi terhadap perbaikan "
"berkelanjutan ini berarti bahwa ketika Anda menggunakan Convertica, Anda "
"selalu mendapatkan versi terbaik dari platform kami—dan kami sudah bekerja "
"untuk membuatnya lebih baik lagi."

msgid "Tools icon"
msgstr "Ikon alat"

msgid "What We Offer"
msgstr "Apa yang Kami Tawarkan"

msgid "PDF Conversion"
msgstr "Konversi PDF"

msgid ""
"Convert PDFs to Word, Excel, and JPG formats, or create PDFs from various "
"file types. Fast, accurate, and reliable conversions every time."
msgstr ""
"Konversi PDF ke format Word, Excel, dan JPG, atau buat PDF dari berbagai "
"jenis file. Konversi cepat, akurat, dan andal setiap saat."

msgid "PDF Editing"
msgstr "Edit PDF"

msgid ""
"Rotate, crop, add watermarks, and insert page numbers. Edit your PDFs with "
"precision and ease."
msgstr ""
"Putar, potong, tambahkan watermark, dan sisipkan nomor halaman. Edit PDF "
"Anda dengan presisi dan kemudahan."

msgid "PDF Organization"
msgstr "Organisasi PDF"

msgid ""
"Merge, split, extract, remove, and organize pages. Manage your PDF documents "
"efficiently."
msgstr ""
"Gabungkan, pisahkan, ekstrak, hapus, dan atur halaman. Kelola dokumen PDF "
"Anda dengan efisien."

msgid "PDF Security"
msgstr "Keamanan PDF"

msgid ""
"Protect your documents with password encryption or unlock secured PDFs when "
"needed."
msgstr ""
"Lindungi dokumen Anda dengan enkripsi kata sandi atau buka kunci PDF yang "
"dilindungi saat diperlukan."

msgid "Star icon"
msgstr "Ikon bintang"

msgid "Why Choose Convertica"
msgstr "Mengapa Memilih Convertica"

msgid "Checkmark icon"
msgstr "Ikon centang"

#, python-format
msgid "100%% Free"
msgstr "100%%Gratis"

msgid ""
"All our tools are completely free to use. No hidden fees, no subscriptions, "
"no credit card required."
msgstr ""
"Semua alat kami sepenuhnya gratis digunakan. Tanpa biaya tersembunyi, tanpa "
"langganan, tanpa kartu kredit diperlukan."

msgid "Fast & Secure"
msgstr "Cepat & Aman"

msgid ""
"Process your files in seconds with our optimized algorithms. Your files are "
"processed securely and deleted automatically after conversion."
msgstr ""
"Proses file Anda dalam hitungan detik dengan algoritma yang dioptimalkan. "
"File Anda diproses dengan aman dan dihapus otomatis setelah konversi."

msgid "No Registration Required"
msgstr "Tidak Perlu Registrasi"

msgid ""
"Start using our tools immediately. No sign-up, no email verification, no "
"hassle."
msgstr ""
"Mulai gunakan alat kami segera. Tanpa pendaftaran, tanpa verifikasi email, "
"tanpa repot."

msgid "Privacy First"
msgstr "Privasi Diutamakan"

msgid ""
"Your privacy matters. We don't store your files permanently, and we never "
"share your data with third parties."
msgstr ""
"Privasi Anda penting. Kami tidak menyimpan file Anda secara permanen, dan "
"kami tidak pernah membagikan data Anda kepada pihak ketiga."

msgid "Ready to Get Started?"
msgstr "Siap untuk Memulai?"

msgid "Experience the power of Convertica's PDF tools today."
msgstr "Rasakan kekuatan alat PDF Convertica hari ini."

msgid "Explore All Tools"
msgstr "Jelajahi Semua Alat"

msgid "Get Started"
msgstr "Mulai"

msgid "All PDF Tools"
msgstr "Semua Alat PDF"

msgid ""
"Browse all our PDF tools organized by category. Convert, edit, and organize "
