msgid "Find answers to common questions about Convertica PDF tools"
msgstr "Temukan jawaban untuk pertanyaan umum tentang alat PDF Convertica"

msgid "General Questions"
msgstr "Pertanyaan Umum"

msgid "Is Convertica free to use?"
msgstr "Apakah Convertica gratis digunakan?"

msgid ""
"Yes, Convertica is completely free to use. All PDF conversion, editing, and "
"organization tools are available at no cost. There are no hidden fees, no "
"registration required, and no file size limits on the free plan."
msgstr ""
"Ya, Convertica sepenuhnya gratis digunakan. Semua alat konversi, pengeditan, "
"dan organisasi PDF tersedia tanpa biaya. Tidak ada biaya tersembunyi, tidak "
"perlu registrasi, dan tidak ada batasan ukuran file pada paket gratis."

msgid "Do I need to create an account?"
msgstr "Apakah saya perlu membuat akun?"

msgid ""
"No, you don't need to create an account. Convertica works without "
"registration. Simply upload your file and start converting immediately."
msgstr ""
"Tidak, Anda tidak perlu membuat akun. Convertica bekerja tanpa registrasi. "
"Cukup unggah file Anda dan mulailah mengonversi segera."

msgid "What file formats does Convertica support?"
msgstr "Format file apa yang didukung Convertica?"

msgid ""
"Convertica supports PDF, Word (DOC, DOCX), JPG/JPEG, and Excel formats. You "
"can convert between these formats, edit PDFs, organize pages, and protect "
"your documents with passwords."
msgstr ""
"Convertica mendukung format PDF, Word (DOC, DOCX), JPG/JPEG, dan Excel. Anda "
"dapat mengonversi antar format ini, mengedit PDF, mengatur halaman, dan "
"melindungi dokumen Anda dengan kata sandi."

msgid "Is there a file size limit?"
msgstr "Apakah ada batasan ukuran file?"

msgid ""
"No, there are no file size limits on Convertica. You can process files of "
"any size, from small documents to large PDF files."
msgstr ""
"Tidak, tidak ada batasan ukuran file di Convertica. Anda dapat memproses "
"file ukuran apa pun, dari dokumen kecil hingga file PDF besar."

msgid "Conversion Questions"
msgstr "Pertanyaan Konversi"

msgid "How do I convert PDF to Word without losing formatting?"
msgstr "Bagaimana cara mengonversi PDF ke Word tanpa kehilangan pemformatan?"

msgid ""
"To convert PDF to Word without losing formatting, use Convertica's PDF to "
"Word converter. Simply upload your PDF file, and our advanced conversion "
"engine preserves text formatting, images, tables, and layout. The conversion "
"maintains fonts, colors, spacing, and structure of your original document. "
"All conversions are free and require no registration."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonversi PDF ke Word tanpa kehilangan pemformatan, gunakan "
"konverter PDF ke Word Convertica. Cukup unggah file PDF Anda, dan mesin "
"konversi canggih kami akan mempertahankan pemformatan teks, gambar, tabel, "
"dan tata letak. Konversi mempertahankan font, warna, spasi, dan struktur "
"dokumen asli Anda. Semua konversi gratis dan tidak memerlukan registrasi."

msgid "How do I convert PDF to Word?"
msgstr "Bagaimana cara mengonversi PDF ke Word?"

msgid ""
"To convert PDF to Word, simply upload your PDF file using the upload button "
"or drag and drop it into the upload zone. Click the convert button and wait "
"for the conversion to complete. Download your converted Word document using "
"the download button. The conversion is free and requires no registration."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonversi PDF ke Word, cukup unggah file PDF Anda menggunakan tombol "
"unggah atau seret dan lepas ke zona unggah. Klik tombol konversi dan tunggu "
"hingga konversi selesai. Unduh dokumen Word yang telah dikonversi "
"menggunakan tombol unduh. Konversi gratis dan tidak memerlukan registrasi."

msgid "How do I convert Word to PDF?"
msgstr "Bagaimana cara mengonversi Word ke PDF?"

msgid ""
"Upload your Word document (.doc or .docx), click convert, and download your "
"PDF. The conversion preserves formatting and layout of your original "
"document."
msgstr ""
"Unggah dokumen Word Anda (.doc atau .docx), klik konversi, dan unduh PDF "
"Anda. Konversi mempertahankan pemformatan dan tata letak dokumen asli Anda."

msgid "Can I convert PDF to JPG?"
msgstr "Bisakah saya mengonversi PDF ke JPG?"

msgid ""
"Yes, you can convert PDF pages to JPG images. Select the page you want to "
"convert or convert all pages. You can also choose the image quality (DPI) "
"from 72 to 600."
msgstr ""
"Ya, Anda dapat mengonversi halaman PDF ke gambar JPG. Pilih halaman yang "
"ingin Anda konversi atau konversi semua halaman. Anda juga dapat memilih "
"kualitas gambar (DPI) dari 72 hingga 600."

msgid "How do I convert images to PDF?"
msgstr "Bagaimana cara mengonversi gambar ke PDF?"

msgid ""
"Upload one or multiple JPG/JPEG images, arrange them in the desired order, "
"and click convert. All images will be combined into a single PDF document "
"with automatic A4 formatting."
msgstr ""
"Unggah satu atau beberapa gambar JPG/JPEG, atur dalam urutan yang "
"diinginkan, dan klik konversi. Semua gambar akan digabungkan menjadi satu "
"dokumen PDF dengan pemformatan A4 otomatis."

msgid "Can I extract tables from PDF to Excel?"
msgstr "Bisakah saya mengekstrak tabel dari PDF ke Excel?"

msgid ""
"Yes, you can extract tables from PDF files and convert them to Excel format. "
"Upload your PDF, and Convertica will extract all tables and save them in an "
"Excel file."
msgstr ""
"Ya, Anda dapat mengekstrak tabel dari file PDF dan mengonversinya ke format "
"Excel. Unggah PDF Anda, dan Convertica akan mengekstrak semua tabel dan "
"menyimpannya dalam file Excel."

msgid "Editing & Organization"
msgstr "Pengeditan & Organisasi"

msgid "How do I merge PDF online free without watermark?"
msgstr "Bagaimana cara menggabungkan PDF online gratis tanpa watermark?"

msgid ""
"To merge PDF online free without watermark, use Convertica's PDF merger. Go "
"to the Merge PDF page, select multiple PDF files, arrange them in the "
"desired order using drag and drop, and click merge. All selected files will "
"be combined into a single PDF document with no watermark added. The merged "
"PDF maintains the quality of original files."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggabungkan PDF online gratis tanpa watermark, gunakan penggabung "
"PDF Convertica. Buka halaman Gabungkan PDF, pilih beberapa file PDF, atur "
"dalam urutan yang diinginkan menggunakan drag and drop, dan klik gabungkan. "
"Semua file yang dipilih akan digabungkan menjadi satu dokumen PDF tanpa "
"watermark. PDF yang digabungkan mempertahankan kualitas file asli."

msgid "How do I merge multiple PDF files?"
msgstr "Bagaimana cara menggabungkan beberapa file PDF?"

msgid ""
"To merge PDF files, go to the Merge PDF page, select multiple PDF files, "
"arrange them in the desired order using drag and drop, and click merge. All "
"selected files will be combined into a single PDF document."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggabungkan file PDF, buka halaman Gabungkan PDF, pilih beberapa "
"file PDF, atur dalam urutan yang diinginkan menggunakan drag and drop, dan "
"klik gabungkan. Semua file yang dipilih akan digabungkan menjadi satu "
"dokumen PDF."

msgid "Can I split a PDF into separate files?"
msgstr "Bisakah saya memisahkan PDF menjadi file terpisah?"

msgid ""
"Yes, you can split a PDF into separate files. Upload your PDF, choose how to "
"split it (by page range or every N pages), and download the resulting files."
msgstr ""
"Ya, Anda dapat memisahkan PDF menjadi file terpisah. Unggah PDF Anda, pilih "
"cara memisahkannya (berdasarkan rentang halaman atau setiap N halaman), dan "
"unduh file hasilnya."

msgid "How do I compress PDF to under 1MB for email?"
msgstr "Bagaimana cara mengompres PDF di bawah 1MB untuk email?"

msgid ""
"To compress PDF to under 1MB for email, use Convertica's PDF compressor. "
"Upload your PDF file, select the high compression level, and click compress. "
"The tool will reduce the file size while maintaining acceptable quality for "
"email attachments. You can preview the compressed file size before "
"downloading."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengompres PDF di bawah 1MB untuk email, gunakan kompresor PDF "
"Convertica. Unggah file PDF Anda, pilih tingkat kompresi tinggi, dan klik "
"kompres. Alat ini akan mengurangi ukuran file sambil mempertahankan kualitas "
"yang dapat diterima untuk lampiran email. Anda dapat melihat pratinjau "
"ukuran file yang dikompresi sebelum mengunduh."

msgid "How do I compress a PDF file?"
msgstr "Bagaimana cara mengompres file PDF?"

msgid ""
"Upload your PDF file, select the compression level (low, medium, or high), "
"and click compress. The file size will be reduced while maintaining "
"acceptable quality."
msgstr ""
"Unggah file PDF Anda, pilih tingkat kompresi (rendah, sedang, atau tinggi), "
"dan klik kompres. Ukuran file akan dikurangi sambil mempertahankan kualitas "
"yang dapat diterima."

msgid "Can I rotate PDF pages?"
msgstr "Bisakah saya memutar halaman PDF?"

msgid ""
"Yes, you can rotate PDF pages by 90, 180, or 270 degrees. Select the pages "
"you want to rotate and choose the rotation angle."
msgstr ""
"Ya, Anda dapat memutar halaman PDF sebesar 90, 180, atau 270 derajat. Pilih "
"halaman yang ingin Anda putar dan pilih sudut rotasi."

msgid "How do I add a watermark to PDF?"
msgstr "Bagaimana cara menambahkan watermark ke PDF?"

msgid ""
"Upload your PDF, choose between text or image watermark, set the position "
"and transparency, and apply. The watermark will be added to all pages or "
"selected pages."
msgstr ""
"Unggah PDF Anda, pilih antara watermark teks atau gambar, atur posisi dan "
"transparansi, dan terapkan. Watermark akan ditambahkan ke semua halaman atau "
"halaman yang dipilih."

msgid "Security & Privacy"
msgstr "Keamanan & Privasi"

msgid "Is my data secure?"
msgstr "Apakah data saya aman?"

msgid ""
"Yes, your data is secure. All files are processed securely and automatically "
"deleted immediately after conversion. We do not store your files, and your "
"privacy is our top priority. You can also protect your PDFs with password "
"encryption."
msgstr ""
"Ya, data Anda aman. Semua file diproses dengan aman dan dihapus otomatis "
"segera setelah konversi. Kami tidak menyimpan file Anda, dan privasi Anda "
"adalah prioritas utama kami. Anda juga dapat melindungi PDF Anda dengan "
"enkripsi kata sandi."

msgid "How do I protect a PDF with a password?"
msgstr "Bagaimana cara melindungi PDF dengan kata sandi?"

msgid ""
"Upload your PDF, enter a password (and optionally an owner password), and "
"click protect. The PDF will be encrypted and require a password to open."
msgstr ""
"Unggah PDF Anda, masukkan kata sandi (dan opsional kata sandi pemilik), dan "
"klik lindungi. PDF akan dienkripsi dan memerlukan kata sandi untuk dibuka."

msgid "Can I remove password protection from a PDF?"
msgstr "Bisakah saya menghapus perlindungan kata sandi dari PDF?"

msgid ""
"Yes, if you know the password, you can unlock a protected PDF. Upload the "
"protected PDF, enter the password, and click unlock. The password protection "
"will be removed."
msgstr ""
"Ya, jika Anda tahu kata sandinya, Anda dapat membuka kunci PDF yang "
"dilindungi. Unggah PDF yang dilindungi, masukkan kata sandi, dan klik buka "
"kunci. Perlindungan kata sandi akan dihapus."

msgid "Are my files stored on your servers?"
msgstr "Apakah file saya disimpan di server Anda?"

msgid ""
"No, your files are not stored on our servers. Files are processed "
"immediately and automatically deleted after conversion. We do not keep "
"copies of your documents."
msgstr ""
"Tidak, file Anda tidak disimpan di server kami. File diproses segera dan "
"dihapus otomatis setelah konversi. Kami tidak menyimpan salinan dokumen Anda."

msgid "Technical Questions"
msgstr "Pertanyaan Teknis"

msgid "What browsers are supported?"
msgstr "Browser apa yang didukung?"

msgid ""
"Convertica works on all modern browsers including Chrome, Firefox, Safari, "
"Edge, and Opera. The website is also mobile-friendly and works on "
"smartphones and tablets."
msgstr ""
"Convertica bekerja di semua browser modern termasuk Chrome, Firefox, Safari, "
"Edge, dan Opera. Situs web ini juga ramah seluler dan bekerja di smartphone "
"dan tablet."

msgid "How long does conversion take?"
msgstr "Berapa lama waktu yang dibutuhkan untuk konversi?"

msgid ""
"Conversion time depends on file size and complexity. Most conversions "
"complete in seconds. Larger files may take a minute or two. The progress is "
"shown during conversion."
msgstr ""
"Waktu konversi bergantung pada ukuran dan kompleksitas file. Sebagian besar "
"konversi selesai dalam hitungan detik. File yang lebih besar mungkin "
"membutuhkan satu atau dua menit. Kemajuan ditampilkan selama konversi."

msgid "What if conversion fails?"
msgstr "Bagaimana jika konversi gagal?"

msgid ""
"If conversion fails, please check that your file is not corrupted and is in "
"a supported format. Try again, and if the problem persists, contact our "
"support team."
msgstr ""
"Jika konversi gagal, harap periksa bahwa file Anda tidak rusak dan dalam "
"format yang didukung. Coba lagi, dan jika masalah berlanjut, hubungi tim "
"dukungan kami."

msgid "Can I use Convertica on mobile devices?"
msgstr "Bisakah saya menggunakan Convertica di perangkat seluler?"

msgid ""
"Yes, Convertica is fully responsive and works on mobile devices. You can "
"convert, edit, and organize PDFs directly from your smartphone or tablet."
msgstr ""
"Ya, Convertica sepenuhnya responsif dan bekerja di perangkat seluler. Anda "
"dapat mengonversi, mengedit, dan mengatur PDF langsung dari smartphone atau "
"tablet Anda."

msgid "Still have questions?"
msgstr "Masih ada pertanyaan?"

msgid ""
"If you couldn't find the answer you're looking for, feel free to contact us."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda tidak dapat menemukan jawaban yang Anda cari, jangan ragu untuk "
"menghubungi kami."

msgid "Breadcrumb"
msgstr "Breadcrumb"

msgid "We use cookies to enhance your experience and analyze traffic."
msgstr ""
"Kami menggunakan cookie untuk meningkatkan pengalaman Anda dan menganalisis "
"lalu lintas."

msgid "Reject All"
msgstr "Tolak Semua"

msgid "Customize"
msgstr "Sesuaikan"

msgid "Accept All"
msgstr "Terima Semua"

msgid "Cookie Preferences"
msgstr "Preferensi Cookie"

msgid ""
"Manage your cookie preferences. You can enable or disable different types of "
"cookies below. Essential cookies cannot be disabled as they are necessary "
"for the website to function."
msgstr ""
"Kelola preferensi cookie Anda. Anda dapat mengaktifkan atau menonaktifkan "
"jenis cookie yang berbeda di bawah. Cookie esensial tidak dapat "
"dinonaktifkan karena diperlukan agar situs web berfungsi."

msgid "Essential Cookies"
msgstr "Cookie Esensial"

msgid ""
"Required for the website to function properly. These cookies enable core "
"functionality such as security, network management, and accessibility. They "
"cannot be disabled."
msgstr ""
"Dibutuhkan agar situs web berfungsi dengan baik. Cookie ini mengaktifkan "
"fungsionalitas inti seperti keamanan, manajemen jaringan, dan aksesibilitas. "
"Cookie ini tidak dapat dinonaktifkan."

msgid "Examples: Session management, CSRF protection, language preferences"
msgstr "Contoh: manajemen sesi, perlindungan CSRF, preferensi bahasa"

msgid "Always Active"
msgstr "Selalu Aktif"

msgid "Analytics Cookies"
msgstr "Cookie Analitik"

msgid ""
"Help us understand how visitors interact with our website by collecting and "
"reporting information anonymously."
msgstr ""
"Membantu kami memahami bagaimana pengunjung berinteraksi dengan situs web "
"kami dengan mengumpulkan dan melaporkan informasi secara anonim."

msgid "Examples: Page views, time spent on site, error tracking"
msgstr ""
"Contoh: tampilan halaman, waktu yang dihabiskan di situs, pelacakan kesalahan"

msgid "Enable Analytics Cookies"
msgstr "Aktifkan Cookie Analitik"

msgid "Marketing Cookies"
msgstr "Cookie Pemasaran"

msgid ""
"Used to deliver personalized advertisements and track campaign "
"effectiveness. These cookies may be set by advertising partners."
msgstr ""
"Digunakan untuk menyampaikan iklan yang dipersonalisasi dan melacak "
"efektivitas kampanye. Cookie ini mungkin ditetapkan oleh mitra periklanan."

msgid "Examples: Ad targeting, conversion tracking, remarketing"
msgstr "Contoh: penargetan iklan, pelacakan konversi, pemasaran ulang"

msgid "Enable Marketing Cookies"
msgstr "Aktifkan Cookie Pemasaran"

msgid ""
"Your preferences will be saved and remembered for future visits. You can "
